</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_407" id="203r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_407_r1l17">
<del rend="strikethrough">Burggraf Joh </del> <expan>VVılh<ex>elm</ex></expan> von Meyental <expan>hofmeiſt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_407_r1l19">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_407_r1l18"><expan>lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> her <expan>hofmeiſt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab></add> vns hat fürgelegt fricʒ Strobell vnſer diener </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_407_r1l20">vvie daʒ Jm Cuncʒ Schücʒ des Heincʒen Schücʒen ſun 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> diener </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_407_r1l21">vnd des hanſen Meyentalers knehte / vvılhelm Strobell <expan>ſeıne<ex>n</ex></expan> Sun </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_407_r1l22">der / beẏ Jm in ſeiner koſt ſeẏ / gefangen vnd Jm gelt auſʒ <expan>ſeın<ex>er</ex></expan> taſchen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_407_r1l23">vnd auch ein pancʒer das des <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> dieners ſeẏ genomen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_407_r1l24">des Er doch vnbeſorgt vor Jn 
<del rend="strikethrough">beſorgt </del> gevveſen ſeẏ / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_407_line_1576479406895_125">
<del rend="strikethrough">von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan></del> mit den 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_407_r1l25"><expan>ſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> dıe das getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſchicke<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>beſtelle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_407_r1l28">wöllet / daʒ ſie des <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> burgers </del> dıeners ſun ledig laſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_407_r1l29">vnd Jm 
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd </del> das ſein <expan>widergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_407" id="203r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan> von Meyental,
                            <expan>hofmeist<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><add><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> her
                            <expan>hofmeist<ex>er</ex></expan></add>. uns hat fürgelegt Fricz
                        Strobell, unser diener, wie daz im Cuncz Schücz, des Heinczen Schüczen sun
                        und des Hansen Meyentalers knehte, Wilhelm Strobell,
                            <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan> sun, der bey im in seiner kost sey,
                        gefangen und im gelt ausz <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan> taschen und auch
                        ein panczer, das des <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> dieners sey, genomen
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, des er doch unbesorgt vor in gewesen sey.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir mit
                                    den<add><expan>selb<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add>, die das getan
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>bestelle<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, daz sie des
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> dieners sun ledig lassen und im das sein
                                <expan>widergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
